{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"217468c9bc","title":"给周世钊的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"12d0c77c44","index":0,"year":1968,"month":9,"day":29,"articleId":"217468c9bc"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[{"id":"803c8ca1ec","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"217468c9bc","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"前两信都未见，一次是1945年周世钊写到重庆给毛泽东的信未收到，另一次就是1968年周世钊寄到北京给毛泽东的信未见，以致毛泽东表示可惜。"},{"id":"9321edd256","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"217468c9bc","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"批作诗词，无甚意义，不必置理，指1968年，周世钊读到各种毛泽东诗词注释本，致函毛泽东，请问应作何处理，哪些注释本比较好"},{"id":"f7d8baed57","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"217468c9bc","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"对联更抽劣，不可用，指1918年，毛泽东任湖南一师附小主事时手书，由学生刻在竹子上，悬挂在大礼堂的一副对联：“世界是我们的；做事要大家来。1968年，有人建议再写，刻上。毛泽东表示不愿意为个人作纪念。遂此作要。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a2ffd69ef9","type":"title","text":"给周世钉的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"217468c9bc"},{"id":"803c8ca1ec","type":"paragraph","text":"停元兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"217468c9bc"},{"id":"9321edd256","type":"paragraph","text":"此信今天收读，甚感。前两信都未见，三可惜。抽作诗词，无甚意义，不必置理。我不同意为个人作纪念，请告附小。对联更抽劣，不可用。就此奉复，顺祝康好！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"217468c9bc"},{"id":"f7d8baed57","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"217468c9bc"},{"id":"1add11e522","type":"paragraph","text":"九月二十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"217468c9bc"}],"page":{"id":"2e3640f09f","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"217468c9bc","start":309,"end":309}}}},"__N_SSG":true}